2. **Read** this file — **`.cursor/rules/optik-frontend.mdc`** — hot paths and patterns.
3. **Read** **`.cursor/rules/engineering-workflow.mdc`** — plan, approval before code, two options, quality bar.
4. **After every iteration (mandatory):** Review and update if anything changed:
