## Shared / API

- HTTP: `src/shared/api/api/client.ts` — Axios; auto-unwraps `APIResponse` envelope; decode: `src/shared/api/utils/decode.ts`
- Default config: `src/shared/api/defaultConfigService.ts` — `GET /v1/default-config/pages`, `.../tabs`, `.../tabs/:tabId`
